channel.title: How was my last week? | My Site

item.title: My Week from 26.08 to 01.09
item.description: I said goodbye to summer, spent time with friends, and completed my shifts at the warehouse.

item.title: My Week from 24.06 to 30.06
item.description: I went to my hometown to visit my grandmother. I hope the summer will be meaningful.

item.title: My Week from 10.06 to 16.06
item.description: This week I finished the website and laboratory work. I also met with friends. Soon, I will go to my hometown.

item.title: My Week from 30.05 to 09.06
item.description: The week was tough; I passed Mathematical Analysis and Mathematical Logic. I hope for good grades. I still need to pass Operating Systems Architecture and English.

item.title: My Week from 20.05 to 26.05
item.description: This week I was preparing for the summer exams. I hope to pass all subjects without retakes.
